thesis.evolution

Class ThesisProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ec.Problem
      • ec.gp.GPProblem
        • thesis.evolution.ThesisProblem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ec.Prototype, ec.Setup, ec.simple.SimpleProblemForm, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.rmi.Remote, PotentialFunctionProvider

    public class ThesisProblem
extends ec.gp.GPProblem
implements ec.simple.SimpleProblemForm, PotentialFunctionProvider
    The evolution problem of the master's thesis. The object is to evolve a potential function that results in the best possible performance in a small scale combat scenario in StarCraft Broodwar RTS game. Different trees in the individuals are ment to calculate different potential fields: Tree 0: Enemy units Tree 1: Map edges
    Author:
    Oskari Leppäaho
